00:33:47,140 --> 00:33:48,860
 They'll do so well in their job

631
00:33:48,860 --> 00:33:50,820
 and yet they'll do so well

632
00:33:50,820 --> 00:33:53,340
 in glorifying God at the same time.

633
00:33:53,340 --> 00:33:55,980
 That'd be so cool.

634
00:33:55,980 --> 00:34:01,460
 A lineup of lawyers, professors,

635
00:34:01,460 --> 00:34:04,020
 glorifying God in whatever they do.

