00:34:22,300 --> 00:34:27,220
 What is your action telling you

641
00:34:27,220 --> 00:34:29,060
 about what you truly believe?

642
00:34:29,060 --> 00:34:36,060
 Does that make sense?

643
00:34:36,060 --> 00:34:38,340
 It does.

644
00:34:38,340 --> 00:34:46,340
 And my hope to you is that God

645
00:34:46,340 --> 00:34:48,380
 is speaking into your heart today.

646
00:34:49,860 --> 00:34:51,980
 These are the last times.

647
00:34:51,980 --> 00:34:55,140
 There is a sense of urgency.

